Janice SMYTH, Petitioner
v.
CONSERVATION COMMISSION OF FALMOUTH, et al. No. 19-223 Supreme Court of the United States. December 16, 2019

Motion of NFIB Small Business Legal Center, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Appeals Court of Massachusetts denied.
